data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home on a spacious 1-acre lot, offering comfort and ample room to roam. This modern home, built in 2018, features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing the perfect space for a growing family or those seeking extra room for guests. Upon entering, you'll be immediately captivated by the stunning design and attention to detail. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it ideal for entertaining or spending quality time with loved ones—natural light streams through large windows, illuminating the space and creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and abundant storage, making meal preparation a breeze. From casual breakfasts to formal dinners, this kitchen is a true delight for any aspiring chef. The primary bedroom is a private oasis, offering a relaxing retreat after a long day. With its en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet, convenience and comfort are at your fingertips. The two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a home office, hobby room, or space for family members. Car enthusiasts and hobbyists will appreciate the three-car garage, providing secure parking and storage for vehicles, tools, and equipment. And for those who love to tinker or need extra space for projects, the impressive 30 x 40 shop is a dream come true. It offers ample room for your hobbies, storage needs, or even the potential for a home business.
